      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/169955cd5ef0ef077f534c27ce4583035dea0edd.png?auto=compress,format&amp;h=340&amp;w=1200&amp;s=1d5264cfab1753bde1018e3de2ee0df5"&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/19e80bdc443b984db5de92db93ff2f2b0670b1c2.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=crop&amp;h=600&amp;w=1200&amp;s=39119bc744ab28e3f48c27ee19ea1cc1"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Limitless Linux by Pearson&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Level up your Linux skills with the latest Humble Tech Book Bundle with courses by Pearson. Linux offers unparalleled customization, security, and flexibility—all wrapped in a user-friendly, open-source package. Get professional-quality lessons like &lt;em&gt;UNIX® and Linux® System Administration Handbook, Fifth Edition&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Learn Enough Developer Tools to Be Dangerous&lt;/em&gt;, and more. Pay what you want for a whole new user experience on your favorite machine—and help support The BINC Foundation with your purchase! &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a style="color: #EF9741;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;The video courses in this bundle are available through InformIT&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#shellprogramminginunixlinuxandosx"&gt;Shell Programming in Unix, Linux and OS X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#tcpandipillustratedvolume1secondedition"&gt;TCP/IP Illustrated, Volume 1, Second Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt18"&gt;Pay $18 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#comptialinuxplusxk0-005examcram"&gt;CompTIA Linux+ XK0-005 Exam Cram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#understandingsoftwaredynamics"&gt;Understanding Software Dynamics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#systemsperformancesecondedition"&gt;Systems Performance, Second Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bpfperformancetools_linuxsystemandapplicationobservability"&gt;BPF Performance Tools: Linux System and Application Observability&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#linuxessentialsforcybersecurity"&gt;Linux Essentials for Cybersecurity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#linuxcommandlinecompletevideocourse"&gt;Linux Command Line Complete Video Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#advancedprogrammingintheunixrenvironment"&gt;Advanced Programming in the UNIX® Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#unixrandlinuxrsystemadministrationhandbookfifthedition"&gt;UNIX® and Linux® System Administration Handbook, Fifth Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#learnenoughdevelopertoolstobedangerous"&gt;Learn Enough Developer Tools to Be Dangerous&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#apracticalguidetolinuxrcommandseditorsandshellprogramming"&gt;A Practical Guide to Linux® Commands, Editors, and Shell Programming, Fourth Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ubuntulinuxunleashed2021edition"&gt;Ubuntu Linux Unleashed 2021 Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#comptialinuxplusxk0-005certguide"&gt;CompTIA Linux+ XK0-005 Cert Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#linuxtroubleshootingcompletevideocourse"&gt;Linux Troubleshooting Complete Video Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#linuxperformanceoptimizationcompletevideocourse"&gt;Linux Performance Optimization Complete Video Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#linuxfordevelopers"&gt;Linux for Developers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#beginninglinuxsystemadministrationlivelessons"&gt;Beginning Linux System Administration LiveLessons&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#linuxkerneldevelopment"&gt;Linux Kernel Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="shellprogramminginunixlinuxandosx"&gt;&lt;a id="shellprogramminginunixlinuxandosx" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/shellprogramminginunixlinuxandosx_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=6dd0184f29dbf59fd714e740783afad45b727ce98fe7c2da6789d7ae27728112"&gt;Shell Programming in Unix, Linux and OS X&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6e5c8730d88ebd0b5e55112d366b19729ef85d86.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=35e990f447ab1cb16cba4722ca0a9e01"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master the art of shell scripting with this practical guide to programming in the POSIX standard shell. Covering essential Unix utilities, decision-making constructs, quoting mechanisms, and debugging techniques, this book walks you step-by-step through building powerful, portable scripts. With detailed examples and coverage of both Korn and Bash shells, it’s ideal for anyone looking to harness the full power of Unix and Unix-like systems through the command line.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="tcpandipillustratedvolume1secondedition"&gt;&lt;a id="tcpandipillustratedvolume1secondedition" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/tcpandipillustratedvolume1secondedition_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=faa97b753a2b086ed150722c1c55774a3c0cca45ad2dbde1fe721f1b3d0c563d"&gt;TCP/IP Illustrated, Volume 1, Second Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8a83af3cadaa2a866a6b9facddcff60a4e1012d7.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e2401a03811a336ea29261d136307b13"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore the inner workings of the Internet’s core protocols with this detailed, visual guide to the TCP/IP suite. Updated for modern systems and best practices, it explains how protocols operate across Linux, Windows, and macOS through real-world examples. From Ethernet and IP to TCP, UDP, DNS, and security protocols like TLS and IPsec, this book offers a clear, layered understanding of how data moves through networks. Ideal for developers, engineers, and anyone seeking a deeper grasp of reliable, efficient network communication.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt18"&gt;Pay $18 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="comptialinuxplusxk0-005examcram"&gt;&lt;a id="comptialinuxplusxk0-005examcram" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/comptialinuxplusxk0-005examcram_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=b34c31c24143a20ac82e6ec362379b8899f78c596c56087f4e6b615d5463b003"&gt;CompTIA Linux+ XK0-005 Exam Cram&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/616f3b69a219278faa03780795128a2abe3559c4.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=3c5816221849760a0c24763d2ad800b9"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;CompTIA Linux+ XK0-005 Exam Cram is an all-inclusive study guide designed to help you pass the updated version of the CompTIA Linux+ exam. Prepare for test day success with complete coverage of exam objectives and topics, plus hundreds of realistic practice questions. Extensive prep tools include quizzes, Exam Alerts, and our essential last-minute review Cram Sheet.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="understandingsoftwaredynamics"&gt;&lt;a id="understandingsoftwaredynamics" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/understandingsoftwaredynamics_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=49d25721da3f5b1adfd85021d77ee7b2662b9bcc4eb86e5fa55ae982e6f49d52"&gt;Understanding Software Dynamics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/be4af2cb406227c70d4a47ffe19b9d135a3d13c7.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d3e8d15885f8a6341ed82ef7d61a8927"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;When software slows down, fails, or behaves unpredictably, understanding what’s really happening under the hood is essential. This expert guide explores the dynamics of time-constrained software systems, from embedded devices to cloud platforms, offering practical techniques for diagnosing and resolving complex performance issues. Learn to trace execution across CPU cores, analyze system interactions, and design better observability into your code. With real-world examples and a powerful open-source tool (KUtrace), this book equips experienced developers to reason clearly about performance and build more reliable systems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="systemsperformancesecondedition"&gt;&lt;a id="systemsperformancesecondedition" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/systemsperformancesecondedition_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=58336f6aa89da7654c6a9b5004fd33499cb7458ec1ee07b45f4cdb2ceb00727b"&gt;Systems Performance, Second Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4b415407c3a37309f956aee8f303b16432d3d528.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=979574768ac68c6b5334f7b87549c476"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Gain a deep understanding of how systems behave and how to make them faster, more efficient, and more reliable. This updated edition explores performance analysis and tuning across hardware, operating systems, and applications, with a focus on Linux-based environments. Learn modern tools like BPF, perf, and Ftrace, and apply proven methodologies to optimize CPU, memory, disk, and network usage. Whether you're working in the cloud, on the web, or at enterprise scale, this expert guide helps you solve complex performance challenges with clarity and precision.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="bpfperformancetools_linuxsystemandapplicationobservability"&gt;&lt;a id="bpfperformancetools_linuxsystemandapplicationobservability" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/bpfperformancetools_linuxsystemandapplicationobservability_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=c3e33c6b952d8705f98afb6742b3dfcd189e281375ad8923d6531811b059bd23"&gt;BPF Performance Tools: Linux System and Application Observability&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/fdf10e3586a5f6abacdc68a7cbb7477156f25013.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=59b81c4bd63d5ff49db3590b75f40e76"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock deep observability into Linux systems and applications with powerful BPF-based tools. This comprehensive guide introduces over 150 ready-to-use performance analysis and debugging tools, along with step-by-step tutorials for building your own. Learn to trace and optimize CPUs, memory, file systems, containers, and more using BCC and bpftrace. With practical strategies and advanced techniques, this book equips developers, administrators, and engineers to troubleshoot complex issues, improve performance, and gain unprecedented insight into modern Linux environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="linuxessentialsforcybersecurity"&gt;&lt;a id="linuxessentialsforcybersecurity" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/linuxessentialsforcybersecurity_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=3f2067f9c1732fa1ff81134a7b43f9a81f43622dec4e1f81ddc29be4113348b4"&gt;Linux Essentials for Cybersecurity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8d6cafea669b6c2dcde2cfd8d9f663d658031377.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2f55418669e5f62ba0f60cfbcfbf75b6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Leading Linux certification and security experts William “Bo” Rothwell and Dr. Denise Kinsey introduce Linux with the primary goal of enforcing and troubleshooting security. To help you earn certification and demonstrate skills, this guide covers many key topics on CompTIA Linux+ and LPIC-1 exams. Everything is organized clearly and logically for easy understanding, effective classroom use, and rapid on-the-job training.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="linuxcommandlinecompletevideocourse"&gt;&lt;a id="linuxcommandlinecompletevideocourse"&gt;Linux Command Line Complete Video Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3ae4c2bcd97731829260c06c2a8f66b6ab82777e.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=726768d9d6635a42a8e30bc770249357"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Build confidence and efficiency at the Linux command line with over 6 hours of hands-on video instruction. Designed for beginners, this course introduces essential CLI tools and Bash features for navigating the filesystem, editing files, managing access, and automating tasks. Whether you're new to Linux or looking to strengthen your command-line skills, you'll gain practical experience and learn how to explore further using built-in help. Ideal for developers, sysadmins, and anyone working with Linux systems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="advancedprogrammingintheunixrenvironment"&gt;&lt;a id="advancedprogrammingintheunixrenvironment" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/advancedprogrammingintheunixrenvironment_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=baf0ccd2154bf7bfab34b42697ba344e9da8f2b44884009db775859b42627984"&gt;Advanced Programming in the UNIX® Environment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/ad8e5331bdab67f8aefc296ca58f176f05e6a320.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ddf83823ebe9c679d07981f93dae93cb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;A trusted resource for serious C programmers, this updated classic offers a deep dive into the programming interfaces that underpin UNIX and Linux systems. Covering files, processes, signals, threads, and socket-based IPC, it blends foundational concepts with modern best practices. With over 10,000 lines of tested ISO C code and detailed examples across multiple platforms, it’s both a learning tool and a long-term reference. Ideal for developers seeking to write robust, high-performance code that fully leverages the power of the UNIX environment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="unixrandlinuxrsystemadministrationhandbookfifthedition"&gt;&lt;a id="unixrandlinuxrsystemadministrationhandbookfifthedition" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/unixrandlinuxrsystemadministrationhandbookfifthedition_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=612a4917335d807a25b23ac1b058818e5021e857f9528459808a42cc66bdc4b2"&gt;UNIX® and Linux® System Administration Handbook, Fifth Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/4438c4d070e7652456f02654ad5b5584437afd61.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=98c28496c89161607d4f6a93299724bf"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you are managing a single server or scaling cloud infrastructure, the UNIX® and Linux® System Administration Handbook, 5th Edition is your ultimate guide. Trusted by professionals and grounded in real-world experience, it covers everything from networking and storage to automation, containers, and DevOps. Updated for today’s distributions and cloud platforms, this clear, conversational handbook helps you troubleshoot effectively, deploy efficiently, and manage systems with confidence. An essential resource for system administrators, developers, and anyone committed to mastering UNIX and Linux.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="learnenoughdevelopertoolstobedangerous"&gt;&lt;a id="learnenoughdevelopertoolstobedangerous" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/learnenoughdevelopertoolstobedangerous_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=35d3a5d21803f9bdda8c42f59fda6be99b7921fe025c8ff7202096b09875fd73"&gt;Learn Enough Developer Tools to Be Dangerous&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/6e14ce5b9f6382e5e64395fb5b77b427c670726b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=dcd46df74c91b9589bdb3ade03c49686"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn the core tools every developer needs without the distractions. This focused guide introduces the Unix command line, text editors, and Git with just enough depth to make you effective and confident. Through practical exercises and clear explanations, you'll build real technical fluency: navigate the terminal, edit code with Vim or VS Code, write Markdown, manage projects with Git and GitHub, and set up development environments across platforms. Whether you're new to these tools or refining your workflow, this book helps you solve real problems and work like a professional.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="apracticalguidetolinuxrcommandseditorsandshellprogramming"&gt;&lt;a id="apracticalguidetolinuxrcommandseditorsandshellprogramming" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/apracticalguidetolinuxrcommandseditorsandshellprogramming_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=2a4e99db8dbdee4be061f962570a43fd85dd396c0717e95b2cec2550e65a1092"&gt;A Practical Guide to Linux® Commands, Editors, and Shell Programming, Fourth Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3faf0b1ba26572d95b12db150bd7d2ba11d6d7e7.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=04e8c9c945fe4150f43471fbe17ffd3b"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Master the command line with this comprehensive, distribution-agnostic guide to Linux and macOS. Covering essential tools, shells, editors, and scripting techniques, it’s packed with hundreds of real-world examples and a 300+ page reference to 100+ utilities. Learn to work efficiently with bash, Vim, Emacs, Python, MariaDB, and more, plus macOS-specific tools often overlooked elsewhere. Whether you're managing systems, writing scripts, or securing remote servers, this book provides the clarity and depth needed to build lasting command-line fluency.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="ubuntulinuxunleashed2021edition"&gt;&lt;a id="ubuntulinuxunleashed2021edition" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/ubuntulinuxunleashed2021edition_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=a1d1f9e7abea6657baa297b46954c80fd80dbb3a326c899fc3aa604b509e0746"&gt;Ubuntu Linux Unleashed 2021 Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/9569b3f3d3c6de7dfabb0938ea1a507e388cceba.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=f78b0f89a7908564cf572441af9ee98a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unlock the full potential of Ubuntu Linux with this comprehensive and up-to-date guide. Covering Ubuntu 20.04 LTS, it offers in-depth instruction on installation, configuration, command-line usage, system administration, server operations, cloud deployment, and more. Learn about containers, DevOps practices, programming tools, and advanced techniques rarely found elsewhere. Whether you're managing desktops, running servers, or exploring virtualization and automation, this resource provides the knowledge and clarity you need to work efficiently and confidently in modern Linux environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="comptialinuxplusxk0-005certguide"&gt;&lt;a id="comptialinuxplusxk0-005certguide" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/comptialinuxplusxk0-005certguide_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=b1af4e4f642d9db93e3f189ca72553aeda6471a33099537ad0527a574eacf5f3"&gt;CompTIA Linux+ XK0-005 Cert Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/780c004033fc11783af83cf632c32bfa991f4c9c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2f4ac1d3e7089f2cf702452421c79869"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;CompTIA® Linux+ XK0-005 Cert Guide from Pearson IT Certification helps you prepare to succeed on the CompTIA® Linux+ exam by directly addressing the exam's objectives as stated by CompTIA®. Leading instructor and expert Ross Brunson shares preparation hints and test-taking tips, helping you identify areas of weakness and improve both your conceptual knowledge and hands-on skills.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="linuxtroubleshootingcompletevideocourse"&gt;&lt;a id="linuxtroubleshootingcompletevideocourse"&gt;Linux Troubleshooting Complete Video Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/dda592ec0dce0fea9188495e2c991b20e5363143.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=41b01c15a3b04d558249c4e205b44483"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sharpen your Linux troubleshooting skills with over 12 hours of hands-on video instruction. Through guided labs and real-world scenarios, you'll learn how to analyze and resolve issues across servers and desktops. Explore tools and techniques for diagnosing problems in system performance, networking, services, and more. Includes custom scripts to simulate issues, end-of-lesson quizzes, and a scenario-based practice exam to test your knowledge. Ideal for anyone looking to build confidence and expertise in solving complex Linux problems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="linuxperformanceoptimizationcompletevideocourse"&gt;&lt;a id="linuxperformanceoptimizationcompletevideocourse"&gt;Linux Performance Optimization Complete Video Course&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/66adfb2676c237b616d21f03423b648f54998785.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=fe6de8b3279405422a8d2b67cf5f2960"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to analyze and optimize Linux systems with over 9 hours of expert video instruction. This course covers performance tuning from the ground up, starting with analysis tools, exploring tuning interfaces, and applying optimization strategies for various workloads. Through clear demonstrations and whiteboard explanations, you'll gain the skills to improve system responsiveness, resource usage, and overall efficiency across servers and desktops. Ideal for professionals looking to deepen their understanding of Linux performance in real-world environments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="linuxfordevelopers"&gt;&lt;a id="linuxfordevelopers" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/linuxfordevelopers_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=c7fc477f31aae5962855207bf8511f458332cb5f3924ddf3878626cfbfd4b16a"&gt;Linux for Developers&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/dfa2b11cacc59e7086e82dd781514d4b49a24dfc.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=de1800a946d720b21837ce778c11aed7"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're new to coding or transitioning from another platform, this practical guide helps you start developing on Linux with confidence. Learn the essentials of open source software, navigate the command line and GUI, and explore key tools like Bash, Python, Perl, and Git. From editing code and writing scripts to managing projects and building in C, C++, and Java, this book provides a clear, modular path to becoming a productive Linux developer. No prior experience required.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="beginninglinuxsystemadministrationlivelessons"&gt;&lt;a id="beginninglinuxsystemadministrationlivelessons"&gt;Beginning Linux System Administration LiveLessons&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/d4321c541b3a7e87a474c39dafcd66e259216e6a.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=469748c61dd333e04f09c834f32f34a0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn the fundamentals of Linux system administration in just over 3 hours with this practical video course. Guided by expert instructor Sander van Vugt, you'll explore essential tasks like installing Linux, managing files and permissions, working with processes, and configuring services. With real-world examples and a focus on Ubuntu and Red Hat systems, this course is ideal for beginners looking to build a solid foundation in Linux administration, whether on local machines, in corporate environments, or in the cloud.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="linuxkerneldevelopment"&gt;&lt;a id="linuxkerneldevelopment" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/linuxkerneldevelopment_preview.pdf?t=st=1755364414~exp=1755450814~hmac=7f3b21e014c237e92e9df9c3861d9e2a58926400bc5d0f04d7d6bd11bdb29766"&gt;Linux Kernel Development&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/3ac3028da85221d37ae6a872648aefc848d757bb.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=d01cddfe14e069e295280b8cfaf874da"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Explore the inner workings of the Linux kernel with this in-depth guide to its design and implementation. Ideal for developers writing kernel code or anyone seeking a deeper understanding of how Linux operates, it covers key subsystems like process management, memory, scheduling, and I/O. This edition includes expanded content on data structures, virtual memory, synchronization, and debugging, along with practical insights into contributing to the kernel community. Written by a core developer, it blends theory and practice to help you navigate and contribute to one of the world’s most important open-source projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
