ng and pixel-based design&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Process images in high gear with the robust AI-powered Corel PHOTO-PAINT. Enjoy an integrated workflow with CorelDRAW.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
