iththreejs"&gt;3D Data Masterclass: Build Data-Driven Web Apps with THREE.js&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#augmentedrealitymasterclass_buildarwebappswitharjs"&gt;Augmented Reality Masterclass: Build AR Web Apps with AR.js&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#aistudiono-codemagic_generateappswithoutwritingcode"&gt;AI Studio No-Code Magic: Generate Apps Without Writing Code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#3dwebgamelegends_buildbabylonjsgameslikeapro"&gt;3D Web Game Legends: Build Babylon.js Games Like a Pro&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#codefoundations_mastercommandprompthtmlandcssfromscratch"&gt;Code Foundations: Master Command Prompt, HTML and CSS from Scratch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $1 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="micro-frontendfoundations_thefutureofscalablewebapps"&gt;&lt;a id="micro-frontendfoundations_thefutureofscalablewebapps"&gt;Micro-Frontend Foundations: The Future of Scalable Web Apps&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/305b4737dab02c2cae85ed7bc7cc930789d7a8f8.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=fd6574f7b6e1f62a656eb00c9ec55c4a"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;As frontend applications grow, so do the challenges of scale, independence, and maintainability.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course introduces you to the core concepts of micro-frontends—a modern architectural pattern for splitting frontend apps into smaller, autonomous pieces that can evolve independently.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Understand what micro-frontends are, why they matter, and when to use them&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Explore strategies for routing, communication, and code sharing across micro-apps&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Learn integration methods using tools like Module Federation, iframes, or custom loaders&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Discover team-based scaling, deployment flexibility, and performance trade-offs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're preparing to scale a frontend system or exploring future-proof patterns, this course helps you think beyond monoliths and build with modularity in mind.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes lifetime access. Scalable thinking. Real-world structure.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to explore the architecture powering modern teams and large apps—this is your starting point.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="micro-frontendmastery_advancedarchitectureforscalableapps"&gt;&lt;a id="micro-frontendmastery_advancedarchitectureforscalableapps"&gt;Micro-Frontend Mastery: Advanced Architecture for Scalable Apps&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/7f81e476ff9cec258ed678d645ded4608ff92c2f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=e027917be04ebb5ef4ba104c93d9d963"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Scaling frontend development isn’t just about more code—it’s about smarter architecture.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This course dives deep into advanced micro-frontend patterns, showing you how to structure, coordinate, and deploy independently-managed frontend modules at scale—without sacrificing performance or developer velocity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Explore advanced integration strategies like Module Federation, Web Components, and dynamic loading&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Learn how to manage cross-app communication, shared state, and dependency boundaries&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Design deployment workflows for independent teams and isolated builds&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;✅ Navigate real-world challenges: performance bottlenecks, versioning, and UI consistency&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're leading a large frontend team or transitioning to a modular architecture, this course helps you understand how to build scalable systems that stay maintainable as they grow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Includes lifetime access. Real patterns. Real challenges. Real solutions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you're ready to move from theory to implementation—this is your deep dive into modern frontend arch