nding elements, and grounded design. It’s ideal for warehouse districts, industrial parks, or downtown streets.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Box Truck is a vital part of urban logistics whether on the move or parked at a loading dock. This 3D model adds purpose and depth to any film, game or visualization environment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 4 Meters In Scale / High Quality Vehicle &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 24 PBR Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 27 Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unique Handcrafted Vehicle&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Highly Detailed / AAA Quality &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Compatible with Windows, Mac and All Major Software &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 1K, 2K and 4K &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Software:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unreal Engine (5.0 – 5.6)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Blender (Eevee, Cycles)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unity (URP &amp;amp; HDRP)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Houdini (Mantra, Karma)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Cinema 4D &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Autodesk Maya, 3ds Max&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Octane, Redshift, V-Ray, Arnold&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt30"&gt;Pay $30 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="apartmentinteriors"&gt;&lt;a id="apartmentinteriors" href="https://youtu.be/zO2wBfFcvJA"&gt;Apartment Interiors&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Apartment Interiors Kit is ready for world building featuring 299 highly detailed assets, 537 textures and 1,334 meshes. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Design immersive experiences with high quality interiors set pieces optimized for performance across film, game, visualization projects. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Full of props like appliances, cabinetry, wall art, and large set pieces from upscale penthouses and lofts to cozy studios, this versatile highly detailed Kit makes it easy to create rich, elegant, character driven stories.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 299 High Quality Assets &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 537 Textures &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 74 PBR Materials &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 1,334 Meshes &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unique Handcrafted Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Highly Detailed / AAA Quality &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Compatible with Windows, Mac and All Major Software &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 1K, 2K and 4K &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Software:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unreal Engine (5.0 – 5.6)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Blender (Eevee, Cycles)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unity (URP &amp;amp; HDRP)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Houdini (Mantra, Karma)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Cinema 4D &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Autodesk Maya, 3ds Max&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Octane, Redshift, V-Ray, Arnold&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="retailstores"&gt;&lt;a id="retailstores" href="https://youtu.be/iQeWMLCbznQ"&gt;Retail Stores&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Retail Stores Kit brings storytelling to the storefront with 160 highly detailed assets, 650 textures and 844 meshes designed for film, games, and visualization.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into a breezy surf and skate shop, flip through vintage vinyl in a music store, browse the latest trends in a fashion boutique, or explore high-energy environments like a sleek bike shop or upscale luxury brand outlet.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With modular detailed assets and richly dressed interiors, this Kit makes it easy to create cinematic retail environments full of life, personality, and creative potential. This Kit is every director and game developer's dream mall. Dive into retail therapy where storylines come with the receipt in the bag.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 160 High Quality Assets &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 650 Textures &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 89 PBR Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 844 Meshes &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unique Handcrafted Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Highly Detailed / AAA Quality &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Compatible with Windows, Mac and All Major Software &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 1K, 2K and 4K &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Software:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unreal Engine (5.0 – 5.6)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Blender (Eevee, Cycles)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unity (URP &amp;amp; HDRP)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Houdini (Mantra, Karma)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Cinema 4D &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Autodesk Maya, 3ds Max&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Octane, Redshift, V-Ray, Arnold&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="policedepartment"&gt;&lt;a id="policedepartment" href="https://youtu.be/G4eRFaIV9Gs"&gt;Police Department&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Police Department Kit features 108 assets, 620 textures and 390 meshes – dive into the world of modern law enforcement with meticulously detailed interiors and exteriors built for crime, thrillers, and procedural storytelling. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;From the stark tension of the interrogation room to the cluttered desks of seasoned detectives, the lively rookies’ bullpen, and the cold confines of jail cells. This Kit captures every shade of the crime drama spectrum perfect for film, games and immersive projects. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether you're crafting a gritty mystery or a buddy-cop comedy, this Kit gives you the environment to set the scene and tell your story with depth and realism. Perfect for film, games and immersive projects. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 108 High Quality Assets &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 620 Textures &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 85 PBR Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 390 Meshes &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unique Handcrafted Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Highly Detailed / AAA Quality &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Compatible with Windows, Mac and All Major Software &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 1K, 2K and 4K &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Software:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unreal Engine (5.0 – 5.6)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Blender (Eevee, Cycles)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unity (URP &amp;amp; HDRP)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Houdini (Mantra, Karma)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Cinema 4D &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Autodesk Maya, 3ds Max&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Octane, Redshift, V-Ray, Arnold&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="mid-sizesuv"&gt;&lt;a id="mid-sizesuv" href="https://youtu.be/iFJ1fmLAdf4"&gt;Mid-Size SUV&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Mid-Size SUV features a full interior, with 17 meshes, 24 PRB materials and stands at 2 meters in scale. Built for both city streets and suburban sprawl, this high quality vehicle blends performance and practicality in one sleek package. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With its spacious interior and everyday versatility, this vehicle fits right into traffic-heavy roads, bustling parking lots, or quiet family neighborhoods. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Whether it's part of a chase, a background scene, or a character’s go-to ride—this SUV is ready to roll for any film, game or visualization project. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features: &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 2 Meters In Scale / High Quality Vehicle &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 24 PBR Materials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; 17 Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unique Handcrafted Vehicle&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Highly Detailed / AAA Quality &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Compatible with Windows, Mac and All Major Software &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; 1K, 2K and 4K &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Software:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unreal Engine (5.0 – 5.6)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Blender (Eevee, Cycles)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Unity (URP &amp;amp; HDRP)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Houdini (Mantra, Karma)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Cinema 4D &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Autodesk Ma+D13ya, 3ds Max&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt; Octane, Redshift, V-Ray, Arnold&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="stationwagon"&gt;&lt;a id="stationwagon" href="https://youtu.be/MiCXbEAykac"&gt;Station Wagon&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&l